OL,3,CFive per cent council tax hike in
OL,4,CPlymouth as leader promises to 'turn
OL,5,Cthe tide'
OL,7,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report on
OL,8,FPlymouth City Council's financial plan
OL,10,FThe leader of Plymouth City Council
OL,11,Fhas predicted the start of an economic
OL,12,Frecovery - but residents still face a
OL,13,Ffive per cent council tax rise to
OL,14,Ftackle intense pressure on vital
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FCouncillors met on Monday to vote on
OL,18,Ftheir financial plan for the next 12
OL,19,Fmonths - the first time the Labour-led
OL,20,Fcouncil has done so under a Labour
OL,21,Fgovernment for 15 years.
