OL,3,CFive per cent council tax hike in
OL,4,CPlymouth as leader promises to 'turn
OL,5,Cthe tide'
OL,7,F"An indication of things to come"
OL,9,FLeader Cllr Tudor Evans told ITV West
OL,10,FCountry he hopes more money will be
OL,11,Fcoming Plymouth's way to ease the
OL,12,Fburden on vulnerable people.
OL,14,F"For too long, councils like Plymouth
OL,15,Fhave had money taken away from them to
OL,16,Fgive to richer councils elsewhere,"
OL,17,FCllr Evans said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
