OL,3,CFive per cent council tax hike in
OL,4,CPlymouth as leader promises to 'turn
OL,5,Cthe tide'
OL,7,F"This government has stopped that now.
OL,8,FThis year we've had an uplift of
OL,9,F#6million in what they call 'recovery
OL,10,Fgrant' to start to turn the tide away
OL,11,Ffrom the way the previous government
OL,12,Fwas funding councils.
OL,14,F"So I'm hopeful this is an indication
OL,15,Fof things to come. It won't bring
OL,16,Fcouncil tax bills down, but in future
OL,17,Fwho knows, we may see more support for
OL,18,Fservices which we're currently having
OL,19,Fto pay for out of council tax."
