OL,7,FCouncil tax payers face an increase of
OL,8,F4.99 per cent - the maximum allowed
OL,9,Fwithout triggering a referendum.
OL,11,FWith police and fire service precepts
OL,12,Fincluded, this would see an average
OL,13,FBand D property paying #111 more this
OL,14,Fyear than they did last year.
