OL,7,FThis is largely due to continued
OL,8,Fpressure on essential services to
OL,9,Fprotect vulnerable people - adult
OL,10,Fsocial care, children's services,
OL,11,Ftransport for youngsters with special
OL,12,Feducational needs and homelessness all
OL,13,Fneed millions more because of rising
OL,14,Fdemand.
OL,16,F"There is a funding gap"
