OL,3,CFive per cent council tax hike in
OL,4,CPlymouth as leader promises to 'turn
OL,5,Cthe tide'
OL,7,F"There are ways of cutting costs. But
OL,8,Fultimately, many local authorities are
OL,9,Ffacing the same situation. It's
OL,10,Fcouncil tax increases."
OL,12,F"Absurd suggestion"
OL,14,FThe council is facing another
OL,15,Funexpected cost - around #410,000 to
OL,16,Fstage a referendum.
OL,18,FLast week a petition was presented
OL,19,Fwhich automatically triggered a vote
OL,20,Fon whether Plymouth should have a
OL,21,Fdirectly elected mayor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
