OL,3,CFive per cent council tax hike in
OL,4,CPlymouth as leader promises to 'turn
OL,5,Cthe tide'
OL,7,FCllr Evans said a mayor would have "no
OL,8,Fextra powers and no extra money".
OL,10,F"The money that it will cost to have a
OL,11,Fmayor and mayor's office will actually
OL,12,Fhave to come out of council tax and
OL,13,Fservices," he said.
OL,15,F"So it's it's a completely false
OL,16,Fprospectus that's being promoted at
OL,17,Fthe moment, and I'm disappointed that
OL,18,Fso many people have been conned in
OL,19,Fthis way. But it's costing taxpayers
OL,20,Fnow #410,000."
